# Cannabis wholesale in one simple platform.
Nabis is the #1 licensed cannabis wholesaling platform, supplying licensed dispensaries with the largest portfolio of cannabis brands in the world.
[Get Started](https://www.nabis.com/</contact>)
Trusted by 400+ partners, including
![Raw Garden](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5c253860fd28a73e98ee5416/621e3948d30968d7f1c8ce64_Frame%203.png)
![Buddies](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5c253860fd28a73e98ee5416/5f84fa3d8cc4771d5b5e4f65_pbr.png)

## All-in-one platform
### Your one-stop shop for cannabis wholesale.
Nabis offers partners lightning-fast fulfillment, warehousing, payment processing, financing, data analytics, sales, and marketing services to enable more brands and retailers to innovate, launch and scale.
![Nabis BillPay icon](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5c253860fd28a73e98ee5416/652eb52d25920a78253b6fa2_marketplace.svg)
## Nabis Marketplace
Shop over 9,000 SKUs across 300 independent brands, all in one place. 2-day shipping. No minimums.
[Learn more](https://www.nabis.com/</services/marketplace>)
![Nabis BillPay icon](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5c253860fd28a73e98ee5416/654a7f32fe0d7ef8a048d275_Distribution.svg)
## Nabis Distribution
Our software-enabled portal coordinates the entire cannabis distribution lifecycle from production to delivery.
[Learn more](https://www.nabis.com/</services/distribution>)
[![Nabis Capital icon](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5c253860fd28a73e98ee5416/652eb5406d526650483a50fe_capital.svg)Nabis CapitalAutomated invoice factoring solution to turn your invoices into instant operating cash.![](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5c253860fd28a73e98ee5416/654a3590348b96078047d88e_Nabis%20Capital.png)](https://www.nabis.com/</services/capital>)[![Nabis BillPay icon](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5c253860fd28a73e98ee5416/654a328b348b96078044e168_billpay.svg)Nabis BillPayPay outstanding invoices, no account details required.![](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5c253860fd28a73e98ee5416/654a34f166f852147be700ce_Nabis%20BillPay.png)](https://www.nabis.com/<https:/pay.nabis.com/>)[![Nabis Analytics icon](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5c253860fd28a73e98ee5416/652eb54784a70f20368aa9e1_analytics.svg)Nabis AnalyticsTrack metrics and performance across locations and sales reps.![](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5c253860fd28a73e98ee5416/654a343cdf1bc6f671698f6b_Nabis%20Analytics.png)](https://www.nabis.com/</distribution#analytics>)
## Why Nabis?
### An award-winningplatform
#### Instant state-wide reach
Nabis operates over 90 vehicles and 133,000 square feet of warehouse space, empowering suppliers to reach 100% of retailers in lightning speed.
#### Key analytical insights
[Nabis Analytics](https://www.nabis.com/</distribution#analytics>) provides real-time visibility into key sales, operational, and financial metrics. Custom reporting and dashboards tailored to brand specifications are available for development based on individual requests.
#### Scalable software
Nabis offers a streamlined end-to-end platform that scales the industry with top-notch customer service. Our proprietary software makes it easy to compliantly schedule, modify, and track orders while managing inventory and finances.
